						               													<description>Juanito Blockits is a dynamic and super original family game in which the game boards will rotate from one person to another! In each round, the figure indicated by the die must be placed in the game area, in such a way that it completes one or more lines or, failing that, maximizes the number of blocked spaces to prevent rivals from closing them on their turn. Challenge your loved ones and may the best win!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Juanito Blockits is a strategy game designed by Alejandra Pini for 2 to 4 people. The estimated time of each game is 20 minutes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Summary&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Juanito Blockits the game boards will rotate from one person to another. In each round, the figure indicated by the die must be placed in the game area, in such a way that it completes one or more lines or, failing that, maximizes the number of blocked spaces to prevent rivals from closing them on their turn.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Goal&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The objective of the game is to achieve as many points as possible, which can be obtained by completing lines, blocking spaces and specializing in a few figures to achieve high scores, without neglecting variety.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
